      "content": "Hi, I'm on a local school board and we're trying to update our rules about students having phones in class. We need to balance kids being able to contact parents in emergencies with the fact that they're a huge distraction during lessons. Can you draft a formal policy for us? We'd like it to have sections for permitted use, prohibited use, and what happens if they break the rules.",
